[I] Log library for C++

[T] A library of C++ classes for flexible logging to files, syslog, IDSA
[T] and other destinations. It is modeled after the Log for Java library
[T] (http://www.log4j.org), staying as close to their API as is reasonable.

[U] https://sourceforge.net/projects/log4cpp/

